data.title: The George Foreman 4-Serving Removable Plate Grill
data.description: Cook quick and tasty meals for the whole family with the George Foreman GRP360R Grill. The improved George Tough non-stick coating is 3x more durable than previous models, and removes the need for excess oil and butter. Plus, removable grill plates are dishwasher-safe, making cleanup that much easier.
